Message.message: so I am on a journey to ignite the flames
even though the fire fills me with terror
I was scared by what the fire could seem to claim
all my excuses made the fire seem scarier
I avoided the flames until it was too much to bear
now its time to start controlling the fire
now its time to get ready and prepare
the time is gone to just aspire
no more excuses for playing unnecessary games
I will be consumed by these flames
I will become more than I am
